tip.text: Go early! I went there twice around 1pm and they were out of a lot of things. The Truffle fries were delish! Definitely one of the best cafes in town.
Adore the cutleries, interiors & cool looking slayer coffee machine. Enjoyed the coffee with Mr Ginger. :D
